{"tid":1588520,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"蘋果提出的15項關稅豁免中有10項已獲得批准","createTime":"2019-09-23T00:46:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-23T00:46:31.000Z","uid":252013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"d551785bc9773945c335d2e2a8c4e3d80e129772","tid":1588520,"uid":252013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T00:46:31.000Z","msg":"開始鬆下口都係好消息來的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n08:32 根據美國貿易代表辦公室及美國聯邦政府官報(FederalRegister)的文件，在蘋果提出的15項關稅豁免中有10項已獲得批准，此外還對更多電腦零件推遲徵收關稅。<br />\n<br />\n美國政府此舉或可降低進口零件成本，從而方便蘋果及其它規模較小的遊戲電腦廠...<br />\n<br />\n來自秒聞 ‧ 實時財經急報app<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mutemute.com/share.php\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mutemute.com%2Fshare.php&d=ly7kxqs2i5dkBMcnx8uly6CH8iT5eEApQhURqQe1KTk%3D&h=4cf727d7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mutemute.com/share.php</a>"}]}